UnconnectedExtension
public class RightMostExtension<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends GenerationPartialStep<NodeType,EdgeType>

Represents the right most extension of gSpan.

For gSpan just backward edges from the last inserted node, or forward edges staring in nodes of the right most path (path of forward edges between the "root" node to the last inserted node) are relevant.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
